{
  "id": "RAW_8d7dc1",
  "title": "跟着台大李宏毅老师学：别让推理模型想太多",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==&mid=2247708859&idx=1&sn=d8cc610ef62da76134dd2045edd91508",
  "date": "2025-07-01 15:02:27",
  "author": "Datawhale",
  "siteName": "Datawhale",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-spacing: 0em; background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); width: auto; font-family: Optima, PingFangSC-regular, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; word-break: break-word; visibility: visible;\">\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本节课主要讲如何缩短模型不必要的思考过程。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先抛出一个问题：推理（思考）越长，结果越好吗？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">有很多实验针对这个问题做了研究，把大量问题输入给模型，得到推理过程和答案，接着把这些推理的长度和答案的正确率分别作为横轴、纵轴画出它们的关系图，发现两者是负相关的。推理长度越长，正确率越低。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但是这种实验其实并不严谨，实验只能证明推理长度和正确率有某种相关性，并不能证明推理长度变长，正确率会变低。因为可能他们背后还有一个因素，就是问题的难度，当问题越难，模型就更倾向于输出更长的推理长度；当问题越难，正确率也会越低。所以看似是推理长度和正确率之间负相关，但实际是他们都和问题难度是相关的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001317\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/480f60da-beec-413b-852a-8d455f1b3f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d079867-0329-4a99-c2c5-bb0910f61200/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">也有一些实验比较严谨的论文得到结论说，推理长度对于正确率不一定有帮助。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">同一个问题输入给推理类模型5次，把长度最短的标为Group 1，次短的标为Group 2，以此类推。如图，论文尝试了多个思考模型，横轴是不同的Group，纵轴是不同Group的长度。可以发现Group 5的长度和Group 1的长度差距还蛮大的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d9d4daa-be64-4774-c478-96bbaf046200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001318\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/902f9b9d-9eee-49c6-125b-a52ba5227e00/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">下图的纵轴是正确率，发现越长的答案并不是正确率越高。所以这么长的推理过程其实是不必要的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05126ec2-f472-469d-bad6-292d6c088f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5435185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001320\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/22c79e5c-3a82-42de-6c26-8dd44fc08700/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最好的工程师，不是把事情做到完美，而是在有限资源下，把事情做到最好。人工智慧也是一样。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/72d21203-e39e-4950-5fff-3dd8a7872c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001321\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f451f6c-4802-4880-83d6-7ef07c8f7200/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么如何避免模型“想太多”呢？针对上节课的4种教模型思考的方法，这里分别给出对应的避免“想太多”的方法。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/45a077fa-f666-4072-dcad-508a2d0b3100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001322\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c8536159-8fdd-4b18-5b99-dd741775bf00/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一个是CoT方法，教模型做思考。Chain of Draft这篇论文则修改了CoT的prompt，教它不要输出太长。在不太影响正确率的情况下，大大降低了推理长度。不过论文是在Claude 3.5 Sonnet上实验的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/92dc20ec-cec1-4a71-74b8-022239804500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5518518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001323\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5325f46-1efc-43ef-746c-3a130aa08900/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二个给模型推理工作流程，可以直接人为控制，比如让模型采样少一些，beam search时候的N小一些，产生树状结构的时候树小棵一点，等等。就能控制模型的推理长度。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62a959be-bdbe-4205-b4fd-c15a2a4bf400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001324\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04c68f9a-645c-4d38-f465-d2a10254c200/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第三个是Imitation Learning，模型学习教师模型的输出内容。因为教师模型每次采样的输出长度都不一样，可以多次采样，选出其中答案正确但是推理长度最短的那条数据，让学生模型去学，这样就能减少模型的推理长度了。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2c11853b-ad01-4d5a-cc7f-4853aa095e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001325\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9db5ac55-a265-4aab-8cbe-beb34ef4a100/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">还有一个方法叫From Explicit CoT to Implicit CoT，把显式的推理过程变成隐式的。分多阶段训练，一开始是（问题，完整的计算过程，答案），然后慢慢把完整的计算过程中的部分token拿掉去训练模型，最后是丢掉计算过程，直接产生答案。最后模型学会了不输出思考过程。论文在比较简单的任务（数学乘法、GSM8K）上训练，发现有推理过程和没有推理过程的效果差不多。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6d43cfb-28e1-4d87-6e86-37e2b088bc00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001326\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3470b11c-6659-4ba6-3b46-845110298700/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: vis