important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">还可以教模型控制推理的长度，在问题后面加一句“推理长度设定为n”，reward设置为（正确率-目标和实际推理长度差异），如果差异很大的话，模型会得到负面的reward。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/734a6d22-cf49-4ab9-cbfe-28ecf8a9e300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48518518518518516\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001332\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/54f7d037-6a57-47af-bf2a-5a1a29bdd100/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">数学问题上训练，在in-domain的测试集测试，模型输出的长度和prompt中指定的长度的差异在2%-6%区间内，但是在out-of-domain的测试集上控制长度的效果没那么好，但也是有一定控制力度的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8eadf456-b47c-4b05-1e13-f2bf4fb4e900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001333\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ac445fd-8978-4b5e-f613-e15f8a849000/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么控制长度后会不会影响到模型的推理能力呢？图中每个点代表不同的模型，横轴是所用的长度，纵轴是正确率。一些不能控制长度的模型（比如DeepSeek-R1-1.5B，Agentica-24K等），输出长度较长，正确率也很高。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">S1也控制了输出的长度，但是控制的方法比较粗暴，超过目标长度的时候就强行截断，没有超过目标长度就强行让它继续输出（比如加一个\"wait\"）。这个方法在输出比较短的时候正确率很低。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-indent: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果用RL教模型控制输出长度，L1-Exact是说必须要输出设定的目标长度，长了短了都不行，L1-Max是说比目标值长了不行但是短了可以。这两个方法在输出token比较长的情况下，达到的效果和不控制长度的模型差不多，输出token比较短的情况下，比S1要好。说明是可以训练一个控制输出思考长度的推理模型的。</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3522a7ef-1575-4933-71ed-7e1e38772300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001334\" data-original-style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f1eb11d-0dd2-4421-d6c9-78dd1fea5000/public\" _width=\"677px\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 657px !important;\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mcexkg0ru9l\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   <p class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 8px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box; width: auto; font-family: Optima, PingFangSC-regular, serif; word-spacing: 0em; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原视频链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ip3XnTpcxoA</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"weui-msg\">\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "基于实验数据探讨推理模型思考长度与正确率的关系，并提出控制推理长度的有效方法",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "基于实验数据探讨推理模型思考长度与正确率的关系，并提出控制推理长度的有效方法",
  "summary": "文章基于台大李宏毅老师的课程内容和实验数据，深入探讨了推理模型思考长度与正确率的关系。研究发现，并非推理越长结果越好，实验数据表明两者可能存在负相关，这与问题难度密切相关。文章系统分析了四种控制模型'想太多'的方法：修改 Chain of Thought(CoT)提示词、人为控制推理流程、模仿学习最短推理样本、以及 From Explicit CoT to Implicit CoT 的转换方法。在强化学习部分，提出了通过问题难度自适应长度控制和长度惩罚机制，实现在不显著降低正确率的前提下减少冗余推理过程。实验证明这些方法能有效优化模型输出效率。",
